column2: SELECT TOP # S.ObjID, S.z, S.ra, S.dec, SN.sn_#, L1.ew, L2.ew, L3.ew, L1.sigma, L2.sigma, L3.sigma, L1.continuum, L2.continuum, L3.continuum, SNN.sn FROM SpecPhoto AS S JOIN SpecLine AS L1 ON S.SpecObjID = L1.SpecObjID JOIN SpecLine AS L2 ON S.SpecObjID = L2.SpecObjID JOIN SpecLine AS L3 ON S.SpecObjID = L3.SpecObjID JOIN SpecObjAll AS SN ON S.SpecObjID = SN.SpecObjID JOIN SpecLineIndex AS SNN ON S.SpecObjID = SNN.SpecObjID WHERE L1.LineId = # and L2.LineId = # and L3.LineID = # and (S.specclass = # or S.specclass = #) and S.zconf > .# and S.z < .# and SN.sn_# > # and SNN.sn > #
